#	Process
1	Disable the emails and SMS going to the store admin and actual customers.
2	Change the 3rd-party credentials like payment gateway, shipment services, ERP, etc to test mode with test account credentials.
3	Do not enable CRON. In case you are enabling CRON, please ensure all the custom CRONs (defined in crontab and inside Magento) are disabled.
4	Enable Display Demo Store Notice.
5	Create a separate branch in GIT for the demo.
6	Check for any live website URL or any 3rd-party API URLs which are connected to the live website that is hardcoded in the demo files and database. If found any replace it will equivalent demo URL/APIs.
